snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Key Lawyer Drops Out of Defamation Case Against Johnny Depp..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 Adam Waldman, an attorney for Heard's ex Depp, claims they 'intend to discover why' Roberta Kaplan, who co-founded the Time's Up movement, has filed to withdraw from the case.   Jun 16, 2020   AceShowbiz - Amber Heard's defamation fight against ex-husband Johnny Depp has suffered a blow following top lawyer Roberta Kaplan's decision to step down.    The high profile attorney, who co-founded the Time's Up movement, has filed to withdraw from the case, alongside Heard's lawyers John Quinn, Julie Fink, and Davida Brook.         Heard will now be represented by Virginia attorney Elaine Bredehoft.    In paperwork obtained by The Blast, Heard appears to have "endorsed" the decision of her lawyers to step down.    "Ms. Heard does not object to the withdrawal of withdrawing counsel and has endorsed the proposed order granting leave to withdraw," the document states.    A spokesperson for the law firm Kaplan Hecker & Fink LL tells the outlet the lawyers' decision to step down in no way reflect ...

snippet.title: Amber Heard--Why People Still Believe Her--LANGUAGE, RACY HUMOR
snippet.description:
DISCLAIMER:  I mean no disrespect with my humor. Abuse is a very serious issue and I do not make light of it whatsoever.  Sometimes things are so heinous and nightmarish, that coping mechanisms have been known to include dark humor. Hence, this video.
I make no money doing these videos, it's a labor of love and to help others.
I have followed Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's abuse allegation scandal, which I've affectionately dubbed the Song that Never Ends.  There is a plethora of information about  this dating back to 2016 until now.   I encourage all of you to read it and form your own views, but my strong stance has always been that Johnny Depp was falsely accused and is still being Gaslighted by Media and other supporters of Amber Heard, merely because she is a woman.  Being a woman doesn't make you perfect, it makes you human.  The same is true for being a man.
With things like this, as hard as they are to deal with, it's necessary for me to find the humor...otherwise it's all downhill.  On February 22nd, I pray that the Truth will fully come out.  Until Then?  All we can do is wait.
